info.title: QRCode
info.description: Customisable QR Codes. Support for styles, images and more! Bare metal engine gives it incredible speed.
info.x-long-description: This is fast and customisable QR Code generator. It gives possibility for obtain QR code image dynamically in your solution through API interface. Detailed description of usage in available in the Docs section. As this API is at the early stage of development, feel free to ask questions or share your ideas for further directions of its growth.

parameters.name: bg_color
parameters.description: Background color. Transparent/#FFFFFF if not specified.

parameters.name: format
parameters.description: Format of the generated QR. 'svg' if not specified.

parameters.name: gradient_stop_color
parameters.description: Second color for gradient fill style. #000000 if not specified.

parameters.name: outer_eye_color
parameters.description: Outer eyes' color. Inherited if not specified.

parameters.name: gradient_angle
parameters.description: Rotation of linearGradient fill style. 0 if not specified.

parameters.name: outer_eye_style
parameters.description: Outer eyes' style. 'default' if not specified.

parameters.name: inner_eye_style
parameters.description: Inner eyes' style. 'default' if not specified.

parameters.name: image
parameters.description: External image to place on the QR. Not used if not specified.

parameters.name: size
parameters.description: Size of the generated QR code image. 150px if not specified.

parameters.name: remove_background
parameters.description: Clearance area under external image. 'false' if not specified.

parameters.name: quiet_zone
parameters.description: Size of the quiet zone around QR. 4 modules size if not specified.

parameters.name: fill_style
parameters.description: Fill style for the QR Code. 'solid' if not specified.

parameters.name: ec_level
parameters.description: Error correction level. 'M' if not specified.

parameters.name: inner_eye_color
parameters.description: Inner eyes' color. Inherited if not specified.

parameters.name: text
parameters.description: Text to be encoded in QR.

get.description: Generates and returns QR Code. See more in Docs.

post.description: Generates and returns QR Code with custom image supplied in multipart request. See more in Docs.
